videos.description: Frank Mason III thinks he has an easy layup but Chase Jeter has other ideas sending the ball the other way with a monstrous block for Duke.
videos.headline: Jeter's block lets Kansas know scoring won't be easy

videos.headline: Really nice ball movement from Duke than Kansas leads to dunks from Chase Jeter and Landen Lucas
Nifty reverse lay in from Josh Jackson

videos.description: Devonte' Graham cuts into the lane and hits the acrobatic layup for Kansas, who then follow it up with Frank Mason III making the steal and scoring again for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Graham, Mason have Kansas flying in second half

videos.description: Frank Mason III talks about his game-winning shot against Duke and how he hopes Kansas can build off the victory.
